                  Though We do not use cookies in order to track your movement around the web, Our websites (http://www.roadkill.co and http://www.candyroad.co) use Google Analytics to help analyse how users use these sites. The tool uses cookies to collect internet log information and general visitor behaviour information in an anonymous form. The information generated by the cookie about your use of the website, including your IP address, is transmitted to Google. This information is then used to evaluate use of our website and to compile statistical reports on website activity.
